76. Write a simple 'birthday countdown' script, the script will count the number of days between current day and birthday.
<?php
$birthday = "2025-12-10"; // Set your birthday
$today = date("Y-m-d");
$diff = (strtotime($birthday) - strtotime($today)) / (60*60*24);
echo "Days left until birthday: " . ceil($diff);
?>
